HEADWORD: Water snail
<hw>Wa"ter snail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any aquatic pulmonate gastropod belonging to <gen>Planorbis</gen>,
<gen>Limnaea</gen>, and allied genera; a pond snail.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mech.)</fld> <def>The Archimedean screw.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water snake</ent>⟦br⟧
